1
00:00:53,120 --> 00:00:53,800
Finally,

2
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:56,040
the final

3
00:00:57,080 --> 00:00:58,080
step.

4
00:00:59,280 --> 00:01:00,080
I...

5
00:01:01,720 --> 00:01:02,920
can't...

6
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,080
You fool.

7
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:25,680
Why go to such lengths for me?

8
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:26,720
Why bother?

9
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:30,280
Does it hurt?

10
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:32,000
No.

11
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,479
Is it worth it?

12
00:01:36,520 --> 00:01:38,240
It's not about worth.

13
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:40,840
It's only about love.

14
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:45,120
Even knowing that you and Yunyuan

15
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:48,360
have loved each other for a thousand years,

16
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:50,160
as long as you turn back,

17
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:53,640
I will be right behind you,

18
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:55,210
protecting you.

19
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:01,560
I'm back, Diyun.

20
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,720
I have returned to your side.

21
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:06,480
Ling'er.

22
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:08,080
Really?

23
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:10,220
You've really come back to me?

24
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:13,410
Are you really willing to marry me?

25
00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:15,760
I am.

26
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,400
Insolent!

27
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:30,960
Is it because of this girl

28
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:33,770
that you refuse to marry the Dragon Princess?

29
00:02:34,320 --> 00:02:35,760
Just let him have his way.

30
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:38,480
Feelings cannot be forced.

31
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:39,560
Love is love.

32
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:41,160
If there's no love, there's no love.

33
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:42,360
Why must you force him

34
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:44,240
to marry a woman he doesn't love?

35
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:45,480
Silence!

36
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:47,980
A doting mother spoils the child.

37
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:49,840
Where are the Heavenly Guards?

38
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:50,880
Take this woman,

39
00:02:51,040 --> 00:02:52,700
cast her into the Beast Realm,

40
00:02:52,720 --> 00:02:53,840
never to return.

41
00:02:54,160 --> 00:02:54,720
Father!

42
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:55,480
You can't!

43
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:57,680
She is the Dragon Princess, Ao Ling.

44
00:03:02,600 --> 00:03:04,520
So it really is the little Dragon Princess.

45
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:06,360
Since you two are in love,

46
00:03:06,440 --> 00:03:08,760
you shall be wed tomorrow.

47
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:14,160
Hahahaha!

48
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:16,760
Fake. It's all fake.

49
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:18,170
Everything is a lie.

50
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:28,360
Your Highness, you're slacking off again.

51
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:30,800
Ling'er.

52
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,560
We agreed to go see the Star Rain.

53
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:34,040
We'll be late if we don't go now.

54
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:35,160
See the Star Rain?

55
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:35,920
Yes.

56
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,120
Let's go.

57
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:47,020
Princess, you are to wed His Highness tomorrow.

58
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:49,440
You absolutely must not see each other today.

59
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:51,440
Please return to the palace with me.

60
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:53,680
Oh, my Princess.

61
00:03:53,880 --> 00:03:55,360
Please, come back to the palace quickly.

62
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:57,620
It would be disastrous if anyone saw you.

63
00:03:58,880 --> 00:03:59,680
Impudent!

64
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:01,120
My business

65
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:03,160
is not for you to dictate.

66
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:04,760
Forgive me, Princess.

67
00:04:04,760 --> 00:04:06,020
Forgive me, Princess.

68
00:04:12,760 --> 00:04:13,720
You are not Ling'er.

69
00:04:13,720 --> 00:04:15,080
My Ling'er is gentle and kind.

70
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:15,940
You are not her.

71
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,320
Your Highness.

72
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:19,760
I am by your side every day.

73
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:22,480
How could I not be your Ling'er?

74
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:25,360
You're not. You're not!

75
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:29,520
Guards.

76
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:32,300
His Highness is tired.

77
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:35,440
Escort His Highness back to the palace to rest.

78
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:41,080
Insolent! How dare you!

79
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:42,320
You dare hold me hostage?

80
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:43,450
Who exactly are you?

81
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:44,960
I am your Ling'er.

82
00:04:45,080 --> 00:04:45,960
You are not Ling'er.

83
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:47,280
I won't marry you.

84
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,760
The wedding is tomorrow.

85
00:04:49,159 --> 00:04:50,960
You must marry me.

86
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:53,440
You have no choice.

87
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:56,320
It's not up to you.

88
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:04,360
Qingluan?

89
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:05,720
Why are you here too?

90
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,520
Diyun.

91
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:08,080
Stay here with us.

92
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:09,160
Qingluan,

93
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,960
why do you want me to stay too?

94
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,620
This is West Mountain,

95
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:15,160
the blessed land where my Phoenix Clan thrives.

96
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:16,680
I was born here,

97
00:05:16,960 --> 00:05:18,160
and raised here.

98
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:20,680
I will rule the Phoenix Clan one day.

99
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:22,040
Stay here.

100
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:24,440
You can have everything you want.

101
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:25,920
What do you mean?

102
00:05:27,760 --> 00:05:28,560
Diyun,

103
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:30,720
actually, I have always

104
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:32,560
had feelings for you.

105
00:05:33,080 --> 00:05:34,640
After we get married,

106
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:36,159
everything in the Phoenix Clan

107
00:05:36,159 --> 00:05:37,280
will be yours.

108
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:39,240
No, I don't want it.

109
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:41,840
Ling'er is waiting for me to save her.

110
00:05:41,840 --> 00:05:43,440
Isn't Ling'er right here?

111
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:45,159
If you stay here,

112
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:47,760
not only will Ling'er and I be with you,

113
00:05:47,960 --> 00:05:51,159
but you will also gain supreme power and status.

114
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:53,280
No. You are not Qingluan.

115
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:55,010
And you are not Ling'er.

116
00:05:55,159 --> 00:05:56,080
This is all an illusion.

117
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:57,120
You can't fool me.

118
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,960
Even if Ling'er doesn't belong to me,

119
00:05:58,960 --> 00:06:00,080
I must save her.

120
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:11,240
Ling'er.

121
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:13,370
I will definitely find Deity Yanxi

122
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:14,280
to cure you.

123
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,760
This place is lifeless

124
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:31,240
and full of poisonous creatures.

125
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:32,520
Does the Little Princess's illness

126
00:06:32,520 --> 00:06:34,650
require fighting poison with poison?

127
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:38,440
How can anyone live in a place like this?

128
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:40,140
Qingluan sent word today.

129
00:06:40,159 --> 00:06:42,240
She said the Little Princess is sleeping longer,

130
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,970
and the mark is getting darker.

131
00:06:44,280 --> 00:06:45,760
Should we hurry back?

132
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:51,040
I know you can understand me.

133
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:52,850
Please tell the Great Witch

134
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:55,159
that Yunyuan of Kunmi Realm seeks an audience.

135
00:06:55,159 --> 00:06:56,560
So it is the King of Kunmi.

136
00:06:56,880 --> 00:07:00,520
Why have you traveled so far to see this old man?

137
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,800
Please save my beloved, Great Witch.

138
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:04,460
I, Yunyuan,

139
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:06,010
am willing to pay any price.

140
00:07:06,520 --> 00:07:07,160
Oh?

141
00:07:07,760 --> 00:07:08,880
What symptoms

142
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,640
could make the King of Kunmi,

143
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:13,160
who restored peace to his realm single-handedly,

144
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,440
so helpless?

145
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:17,480
I do not know what the illness is.

146
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,840
I only know she sleeps more

147
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:19,760
and wakes less.

148
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:22,320
And her spiritual power is fading day by day.

149
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:23,650
That is indeed strange.

150
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:25,880
Did you bring the patient?

151
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:27,360
She is too weak

152
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,240
to travel.

153
00:07:28,520 --> 00:07:29,180
That is why,

154
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:31,050
I came to ask the Great Witch

155
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:32,480
to return to the Kunmi Realm with me.

156
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:34,120
I haven't left

157
00:07:34,200 --> 00:07:36,360
the Valley of Ten Thousand Insects for centuries.

158
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:38,080
Even if you are the King of Kunmi,

159
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:40,159
you cannot command me.

160
00:07:40,280 --> 00:07:40,880
Wait.

161
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:42,159
I heard that

162
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:44,680
as long as your demands are met,

163
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:46,280
you will leave the mountain.

164
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:48,560
I am ready to hear your terms.

165
00:07:49,159 --> 00:07:50,290
You won't regret it?

166
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,360
I won't.

167
00:07:52,200 --> 00:07:53,440
I will do anything.

168
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:54,880
You said it.

169
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:57,800
My pet,

170
00:07:58,360 --> 00:08:00,480
it has gathered the Five Poisons.

171
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:03,340
It only needs a chance to take human form.

172
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:06,280
I want nine taels of your heart flesh,

173
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:07,940
nine drops of heart blood,

174
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:09,760
and ninety-nine scales

175
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,240
to help it transform.

176
00:08:12,960 --> 00:08:13,760
I agree.

177
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:15,480
General, you mustn't!

178
00:08:15,880 --> 00:08:18,210
How much heart flesh and blood do you have?

179
00:08:18,280 --> 00:08:18,960
He is asking

180
00:08:19,080 --> 00:08:20,320
for the extreme number of nine.

181
00:08:20,320 --> 00:08:22,560
Ripping off dragon scales is excruciating torture.

182
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:24,760
How can your body withstand it now?

183
00:08:24,960 --> 00:08:26,560
Have you thought it through?

184
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:27,690
Do you really agree?

185
00:08:27,880 --> 00:08:28,720
I do.

186
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:29,840
General.

187
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:31,080
I only ask the Great Witch

188
00:08:31,080 --> 00:08:33,159
to return to Kunmi with me to save her immediately.

189
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:34,080
General.

190
00:08:34,559 --> 00:08:35,520
Good.

191
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,159
Come into the valley.

192
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:39,320
Then I will go to Kunmi with you.

193
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:44,159
Yueying,

194
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:45,200
wait here.

195
00:08:45,640 --> 00:08:46,280
General.

196
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:58,160
Please.

197
00:10:49,280 --> 00:10:50,410
Great Witch, please

198
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:53,040
return to Kunmi with me now to save her.

199
00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:54,880
Worthy of being the King of Kunmi.

200
00:10:54,880 --> 00:10:57,120
I will go with you.

201
00:11:01,760 --> 00:11:03,960
This is my new healing medicine.

202
00:11:04,280 --> 00:11:06,410
It stops pain and bleeding instantly,

203
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:08,280
but it is very potent.

204
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:12,450
Thank you, Great Witch.

205
00:11:12,560 --> 00:11:14,360
The pain of carving out the heart

206
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:15,620
and pulling out scales

207
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:17,960
is unbearable for ordinary people.

208
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:20,560
The person you are saving

209
00:11:20,800 --> 00:11:23,680
must be more important than your own life.

210
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:25,690
When Ling'er recovers,

211
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:27,340
I will reward you heavily.

212
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:28,880
No need for rewards.

213
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:31,880
Since you met my demands,

214
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:34,560
I will keep my promise.

215
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:45,880
General.

216
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:47,400
I'm fine.

217
00:11:48,160 --> 00:11:48,960
Tell Qingluan

218
00:11:49,280 --> 00:11:50,480
we are returning now.

219
00:11:50,560 --> 00:11:51,560
A short while ago,

220
00:11:51,560 --> 00:11:52,680
Qingluan sent word.

221
00:11:52,680 --> 00:11:54,880
A mysterious force attacked the Cloud Recesses.

222
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:56,360
Luckily, your barrier held.

223
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:57,440
No major damage for now.

224
00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:58,160
What?

225
00:11:59,640 --> 00:12:00,280
Let's go.

226
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:01,680
Wait.

227
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:05,160
You'll just be throwing your life away if you go like this.

228
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:06,920
And you would drag me down with you,

229
00:12:06,920 --> 00:12:09,450
branding me as someone who breaks their word.

230
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:16,180
This is a healing potion I developed.

231
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:20,260
It can temporarily restore you to your peak condition.

232
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:21,690
Thank you, Great Witch.

233
00:12:21,880 --> 00:12:23,040
There's no time to lose.

234
00:12:23,040 --> 00:12:25,040
Let's return to Kunmi immediately.

235
00:12:34,160 --> 00:12:35,360
Impudent Demon Tribe!

236
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:37,640
How dare you trespass in the Cloud Recesses?

237
00:12:37,640 --> 00:12:39,240
You really have a death wish.

238
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:40,320
Qingluan.

239
00:12:40,640 --> 00:12:42,760
You are nothing but a member of the Bird Tribe.

240
00:12:42,760 --> 00:12:44,960
You're delusional to think you can stop us.

241
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:45,680
Yinfeng.

242
00:12:46,280 --> 00:12:48,480
You've finally shown your true colors.

243
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:57,160
A mere Bird Tribe member,

244
00:12:57,160 --> 00:12:59,220
you really think you're invincible.

245
00:12:59,720 --> 00:13:01,760
We only want to take the Dragon Princess.

246
00:13:01,760 --> 00:13:03,320
Since you refuse to cooperate,

247
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,640
then die.

248
00:13:14,760 --> 00:13:15,560
Qingluan.

249
00:13:29,080 --> 00:13:30,320
Since you're already here,

250
00:13:30,320 --> 00:13:31,850
you're not going anywhere.

251
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:36,360
General.

252
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:37,820
What should we do with him?

253
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:38,880
Take him away.

254
00:13:39,080 --> 00:13:40,140
Guard him closely.

255
00:13:40,640 --> 00:13:42,240
I'll interrogate him later.

256
00:13:49,560 --> 00:13:51,420
The young lady has been poisoned.

257
00:13:51,560 --> 00:13:53,490
This poison is incredibly potent.

258
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:55,620
It can even devour spiritual bodies.

259
00:13:57,360 --> 00:13:59,290
Great Witch, please save Ling'er.

260
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:20,620
It's actually a curse.

261
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:22,920
King of Kunmi,

262
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:24,720
your beloved

263
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:27,040
cannot be saved, I'm afraid.

264
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:28,160
A curse?

265
00:14:29,360 --> 00:14:30,220
A poison curse.

266
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:32,400
Ling'er said

267
00:14:32,680 --> 00:14:34,960
she chased Yueying to Kunmi as soon as she woke up.

268
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:37,520
When could she have been cursed?

269
00:14:37,720 --> 00:14:38,960
Her poison and curse

270
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:42,250
were simultaneously planted in her soul's imprint.

271
00:14:42,640 --> 00:14:45,040
If I only cure one,

272
00:14:45,920 --> 00:14:47,980
the other will trigger immediately.

273
00:14:49,160 --> 00:14:51,680
Her body will be instantly damaged,

274
00:14:52,920 --> 00:14:57,160
and her soul will be shattered.

275
00:15:01,280 --> 00:15:03,240
Please, Great Witch, save my Ling'er.

276
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:04,570
I'll agree to anything.

277
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:21,560
I can only suppress it for now.

278
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:25,570
Thank you, Great Witch.

279
00:15:27,760 --> 00:15:28,560
General.

280
00:15:28,640 --> 00:15:30,360
Yinfeng is demanding to see you.

281
00:15:30,360 --> 00:15:32,960
He says he has something important to tell you.

282
00:15:33,680 --> 00:15:34,520
Let me out!

283
00:15:35,520 --> 00:15:36,800
Let me out!

284
00:15:38,360 --> 00:15:39,480
Yunyuan!

285
00:15:39,680 --> 00:15:41,080
Where is Ling'er?

286
00:15:56,360 --> 00:15:57,560
You have a death wish.

287
00:16:03,080 --> 00:16:04,480
I have something to say.

288
00:16:05,160 --> 00:16:06,680
If you let me go,

289
00:16:07,480 --> 00:16:08,680
I'll tell you

290
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:11,760
what poison curse the Dragon Princess is under.

291
00:16:11,760 --> 00:16:12,560
Speak.

292
00:16:13,160 --> 00:16:14,680
If you utter a single lie,

293
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:17,800
I'll make you wish you were dead.

294
00:16:17,880 --> 00:16:19,000
Do you think

295
00:16:19,480 --> 00:16:22,610
the Dragon Princess was ambushed only after she woke up?

296
00:16:22,880 --> 00:16:23,810
What do you mean?

297
00:16:24,920 --> 00:16:26,280
Explain yourself.

298
00:16:29,560 --> 00:16:30,920
Your old flame

299
00:16:31,200 --> 00:16:33,800
was cursed by my master a thousand years ago.

300
00:16:34,400 --> 00:16:36,520
When her soul shatters,

301
00:16:36,760 --> 00:16:38,800
that will be the day my master returns.

302
00:16:38,800 --> 00:16:41,000
My master will surely rule the Three Realms

303
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:42,520
and reign supreme.

304
00:16:48,560 --> 00:16:49,320
Speak!

305
00:16:49,880 --> 00:16:51,400
What exactly did you...

306
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:53,400
What curse is it?

307
00:16:53,680 --> 00:16:54,920
Want to know?

308
00:16:56,160 --> 00:16:57,480
Let me go.

309
00:16:58,880 --> 00:17:00,400
Then save your breath.

310
00:17:04,599 --> 00:17:06,280
Let me out!

311
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:08,930
Just stay in this Qiankun Cauldron

312
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:10,960
and enjoy yourself.
